{"id":5721,"date":"2024-02-14T12:01:29","date_gmt":"2020-02-14T06:31:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=5721"},"modified":"2023-05-30T00:21:40","modified_gmt":"2023-05-29T18:51:40","slug":"modern-bedroom-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Style It Up! Stellar Modern Bedroom Designs for Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Bedrooms with modern aesthetics are all about keeping it simple and clean. How do you balance style and comfort at the same time? Take a look at these modern bedroom designs to know more!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes a design tick? We say, to each his\/her own! While each one of us have preferences when it comes to our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/\">bedroom interior design<\/a>, the thing all of us have in common is the undeniable urge to keep it effortlessly stylish and cosy. Check out these stunning bedroom design ideas for some inspiration!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep It Antique With This Modern Bedroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There is no reason why your bedroom cannot look modern and timeless at the same time. This modern bedroom design has been tastefully kept minimal with a subtle colour palette and modest decor. What makes it stand out are inspired additions like the vintage telephone, rustic frames and elements with traditional motif designs. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005134\/modern-bedroom-designs-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom designs where your bedroom cannot look modern and timeless at the same time\" class=\"wp-image-5725\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005134\/modern-bedroom-designs-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005134\/modern-bedroom-designs-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005134\/modern-bedroom-designs-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005134\/modern-bedroom-designs-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Sophistication With This Modern Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Soothing colours coupled with rich textures are all that a modern bedroom needs. This design is a testimony to that. The monotony of greys and whites is broken with the right amount of blue. Pendant lights on either side keep the interior design of this bedroom sophisticated. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005138\/modern-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom with rich textures are all that a modern bedroom needs\" class=\"wp-image-5726\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005138\/modern-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005138\/modern-bedroom-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005138\/modern-bedroom-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005138\/modern-bedroom-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"5 Modern Bedroom Designs that are High on Style | Bedroom Design | Home Interiors | DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Hn9q-MFwktA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Comfort Is In The Classics Of The Modern Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Warm lights, natural browns and soothing textures &#8211; it doesn&#8217;t get more classic than this! Add to that the right designer decor and you have a masterpiece of a bedroom to live in! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005142\/modern-bedroom-ideas-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom ideas where  it doesn't get more classic than this modern master bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-5727\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005142\/modern-bedroom-ideas-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005142\/modern-bedroom-ideas-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005142\/modern-bedroom-ideas-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005142\/modern-bedroom-ideas-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Balance style and comfort with modern bedroom designs!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15145556\/balance-style-and-comfort-with-modern-bedroom-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pastel Glamour<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Undeniably modern and undeniably cool, colour blocking with a pastel hue is refreshing for modern bedroom design. A singular grey wall helps tone down overall brightness. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005149\/modern-bedroom-interior-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom interior where colour blocking with a pastel hue is refreshing for your modern bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-5729\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005149\/modern-bedroom-interior-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005149\/modern-bedroom-interior-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005149\/modern-bedroom-interior-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005149\/modern-bedroom-interior-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Royal Emerald <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Let this design be an inspiration of how monochromes can bring in a magical effect. Emerald green along with sophisticated textures and patterns make this modern bedroom design seem fit for royalty. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005145\/modern-bedroom-interior-design-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom interior design where design be an inspiration of how monochromes can bring some modern bedroom design ideas\" class=\"wp-image-5728\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005145\/modern-bedroom-interior-design-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005145\/modern-bedroom-interior-design-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005145\/modern-bedroom-interior-design-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005145\/modern-bedroom-interior-design-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Striped Effect<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern bedroom design has us feeling therapeutic with its vertical striped theme. We love how the textures and accents complement the pattern. What also stands out is how the use of subtle tones of primary colours allow the overall design to go easy on the eyes! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005127\/modern-bedroom-colors-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom colours  which has us feeling therapeutic with its vertical striped theme with these modern bedroom images\" class=\"wp-image-5723\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005127\/modern-bedroom-colors-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005127\/modern-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005127\/modern-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005127\/modern-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pop of Colour In A Modern Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A little bit of quirk didn&#8217;t hurt anybody! This modern bedroom design has its base in a neutral white and is enhanced by a quirky play of colours throughout the decor. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005200\/modern-master-bedroom-design-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern master bedroom design which has its base in a neutral white\" class=\"wp-image-5732\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005200\/modern-master-bedroom-design-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005200\/modern-master-bedroom-design-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005200\/modern-master-bedroom-design-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005200\/modern-master-bedroom-design-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Striking Contrast Of A Modern Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The colour blue and its many hues are generally a safe bet, and a beautiful one at that for a modern bedroom design. You can make things interesting by adding a dash of a contrasting colour to brighten up the space. Notice how a study unit in blue is placed right opposite a wardrobe in white? The contrast is simply striking and definately a choice for modern homeowners.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005157\/modern-luxury-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern luxury bedroom where you can make things interesting by adding a dash of a contrasting colour to a modern luxury bedroom design\" class=\"wp-image-5731\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005157\/modern-luxury-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005157\/modern-luxury-bedroom-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005157\/modern-luxury-bedroom-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005157\/modern-luxury-bedroom-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Compact Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If smaller spaces push the parameters of creativity, we are totally up for it! The furniture and decor is fuss-free in terms of colour and laminate. A transformable bed cum study table is the real hero of this modern bedroom\u2019s design. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005153\/modern-bedroom-sets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom sets  where the furniture and decor is fuss-free in terms of colour\" class=\"wp-image-5730\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005153\/modern-bedroom-sets-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005153\/modern-bedroom-sets-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005153\/modern-bedroom-sets-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005153\/modern-bedroom-sets-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Which one of these modern bedroom designs pulls of a polished and comfortable vibe, according to you? Let us know in the comments section below. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combinatio